From: Michal Hocko <mhocko@suse.com>
Subject: kabi assert ptrace: slightly saner 'get_dumpable()' logic
Patch-mainline: Never (kabi fixup)
References: bsc#1265308

Add kabi assert for the task struct size after additional bit field.

Signed-off-by: Michal Hocko <mhocko@suse.com>
Reviewed-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>
---
 include/linux/sched.h |  816 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 816 insertions(+)

--- a/include/linux/sched.h
+++ b/include/linux/sched.h
@@ -2385,6 +2385,8 @@ struct task_struct {
 suse_kabi_static_assert(offsetof(struct task_struct, stats) ==
 			offsetof(struct __orig_task_struct, stats));
 
+suse_kabi_static_assert(sizeof(struct task_struct) == sizeof(struct __orig_task_struct));
+
 static inline struct pid *task_pid(struct task_struct *task)
 {
 	return task->thread_pid;
